text: Birnie Duthie (13 June 1905 - 13 April 1994) was a British alpine skier. She competed in the women's combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1905 births Category:1994 deaths Category:British female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Great Britain Category:Alpine skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
